title: Bobby’s $100 Music Memorabilia Challenge + Raymundo's Mask Selfie + Ask Arkansas Keith: Wild Duck Eggs
itunes:title: Bobby’s $100 Music Memorabilia Challenge + Raymundo's Mask Selfie + Ask Arkansas Keith: Wild Duck Eggs
description:
Bobby challenged everyone to find him a fun, low price piece of music memorabilia to buy. Whoever comes up with the best item gets $100. Raymundo was asked for a selfie by a listener while he was grocery shopping and wearing a face mask. Plus, Bobby’s former stepdad, 'Arkansas Keith' answers a listener question from our voicemail line!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
